@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
    ViewBag.Message = "Learn more about our Car Sales & Inventory System project";
}

<style>
    main {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 3rem auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
    }

    h2#title {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        color: #007bff;
    }

    h3 {
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        color: #555;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        text-align: justify;
    }
</style>

<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <h2 id="title">@ViewBag.Title</h2>
    <h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>

    <p>
        The Car Sales & Inventory System is a comprehensive web application designed to streamline the management of automotive sales and parts inventory.
        This platform allows users to browse a wide variety of vehicles and spare parts, manage orders efficiently, and ensure seamless connections between customers and sellers.
    </p>

    <p>
        The system offers an intuitive user interface, secure login and registration features, and real-time inventory updates.
        Whether you're a customer looking for your next car or a dealer managing stock, this system provides all the necessary tools in one place.
    </p>

    <p>
        Our goal is to enhance the car sales experience by integrating inventory management with order tracking and customer support, making vehicle purchasing and parts shopping easier than ever.
    </p>
</main>
